name: The Consciousness
description:
Everything moves and nothing is stopped, vibration is the way that consciousness permeates the entire reality
of the universe, whether in other worlds, technological or biological celestial bodies and beings, it doesn't
matter, everything is consciousness. And each time we connect more through our senses and knowledge, we experience
and become one with what we call God. So we become Saints, Gods and Demi-Gods by managing to manipulate our own
reality in this vast field of vibrational information, and finally take control of our own destiny!
